text: here. Mother's feet are in the water as it's pouring on the floor, and the window is open. You can see a yard outside. There's a dish and cups on the sink, and the curtains are pulled back so you can see out the window. The cupboard door is open, and they're all fully dressed, and they have sort of a nondescript expression on their face. The woman has her mouth.
